  "markdown": "[Skip to main content](https://universalquantum.com/knowledge-hub#main-content)\n[](https://universalquantum.com/)\n## Main navigation\n  * [Who we are](https://universalquantum.com/who-we-are)\n  * [What we do](https://universalquantum.com/what-we-do)\n  * [Working here](https://universalquantum.com/working-here)\n  * Knowledge hub\n    * [News & Blog](https://universalquantum.com/knowledge-hub/news-blog)\n    * [Technical Resources](https://universalquantum.com/knowledge-hub/technical-resources)\n  * [Contact us](https://universalquantum.com/contact-us)\n\n\nToggle menu\n  * [En](https://universalquantum.com/knowledge-hub)\n  * [De](https://universalquantum.com/de/wissenszentrum)\n\n\n## Main navigation\n  * [Who we are](https://universalquantum.com/who-we-are)\n  * [What we do](https://universalquantum.com/what-we-do)\n  * [Working here](https://universalquantum.com/working-here)\n  * [Knowledge hub](https://universalquantum.com/knowledge-hub)\n    * [News & Blog](https://universalquantum.com/knowledge-hub/news-blog)\n    * [Technical Resources](https://universalquantum.com/knowledge-hub/technical-resources)\n  * [Contact us](https://universalquantum.com/contact-us)\n\n\n[Privacy](https://universalquantum.com/knowledge-hub)  \n[Cookies](https://universalquantum.com/knowledge-hub)\n\u00a9 2026 Universal Quantum Ltd.\n  * [LinkedIn](https://www.linkedin.com/company/universal-quantum)\n  * [X](https://x.com/universalquant)\n\n\n## News & Blog\nOur work is developing fast. Stay up to date with our latest news and publications:\nFilters:\nCompany news\nPodcasts\nTechnical blogs\n### Podcast:The Quantum Rivalry of Schr\u00f6dinger & Heisenberg\nExplore the fascinating parallels between heated rivalries in sports and the intense debates in quantum physics, focusing on Schr\u00f6dinger and Heisenberg.\n[Read more](https://universalquantum.com/knowledge-hub/podcast/the-quantum-rivalry-of-schr%C3%B6dinger-and-eisenberg)\n[ ![UQ](https://universalquantum.com/sites/default/files/styles/landscape_desktop/public/2026-05/Logo%202.jpg?h=8fc98104&itok=K8umKDCh) ](https://universalquantum.com/knowledge-hub/podcast/the-quantum-rivalry-of-schr%C3%B6dinger-and-eisenberg)\n### Universal Quantum appoints Freeke Heijman as Senior European Advisor\nUniversal Quantum, the UK based company building the world's most scalable quantum computers, today announced the appointment of Freeke Heijman as Senior European Advisor.\n[Read more](https://universalquantum.com/knowledge-hub/universal-quantum-appoints-Freeke-Heijman-as-senior-european-advisor)\n[ ![UQ](https://universalquantum.com/sites/default/files/styles/landscape_desktop/public/2026-05/52995517310_bba4d9d357_c.jpg?h=2379611a&itok=ibql1SqM) ](https://universalquantum.com/knowledge-hub/universal-quantum-appoints-Freeke-Heijman-as-senior-european-advisor)\n### Podcast: The Wiring Problem in Large-Scale Quantum Computers\nThis episode explores the challenges of wiring and control systems in large-scale quantum computers, drawing parallels with classical electronics and physics labs.\n[Read more](https://universalquantum.com/knowledge-hub/podcast/the-wiring-problem-in-large-scale-quantum-computers)\n[ ![UQ](https://universalquantum.com/sites/default/files/styles/landscape_desktop/public/2026-04/Logo%202.jpg?h=f697827c&itok=LUx1fMG3) ](https://universalquantum.com/knowledge-hub/podcast/the-wiring-problem-in-large-scale-quantum-computers)\n### Podcast: \u00a32B and What Actually Matters\nThis episode explores the UK government's recent \u00a32 billion quantum funding announcement, delving into quantum technology missions, misconceptions about quantum computing and its potential impact on industry and society.\n[Read more](https://universalquantum.com/knowledge-hub/podcast/%C2%A32B-and-what-actually-matters)\n[ ![UQ](https://universalquantum.com/sites/default/files/styles/landscape_desktop/public/2026-03/Logo%202.jpg?h=e55433bc&itok=0zyp0EBf) ](https://universalquantum.com/knowledge-hub/podcast/%C2%A32B-and-what-actually-matters)\n#### Pagination\n  * [ Current page 1](https://universalquantum.com/knowledge-hub?page=0 \"Current page\")\n  * [ Page 2](https://universalquantum.com/knowledge-hub?page=1 \"Go to page 2\")\n  * [ Page 3](https://universalquantum.com/knowledge-hub?page=2 \"Go to page 3\")\n  * [ Page 4](https://universalquantum.com/knowledge-hub?page=3 \"Go to page 4\")\n  * [ Page 5](https://universalquantum.com/knowledge-hub?page=4 \"Go to page 5\")\n  * [ Page 6](https://universalquantum.com/knowledge-hub?page=5 \"Go to page 6\")\n  * [ Page 7](https://universalquantum.com/knowledge-hub?page=6 \"Go to page 7\")\n  * [ Page 8](https://universalquantum.com/knowledge-hub?page=7 \"Go to page 8\")\n  * [ Page 9](https://universalquantum.com/knowledge-hub?page=8 \"Go to page 9\")\n  * \u2026\n  * [ Next page Next ](https://universalquantum.com/knowledge-hub?page=1 \"Go to next page\")\n\n\n## Press\nWe\u2019re excited to share our work and the potential of quantum computing with all audiences. For all press enquiries, please contact media@universalquantum.com.\n[Download our press pack](https://universalquantum.com/themes/quantum/assets/UQ_Press_Release.pdf)\n## Technical Resources\nUniversal Quantum was founded on ground-breaking research which includes a practical blueprint for a scalable trapped ion quantum computer with millions of qubits.\nWe\u2019re delivering against that plan today, and we continue to drive progress in the field, and to share our discoveries and solutions with collaborators and colleagues.\nHere, you can find a directory of technical resources, published to help drive further research. \n  * [LinkedIn](https://www.linkedin.com/company/universal-quantum)\n  * [X](https://x.com/universalquant)\n\n\n## Secondary menu\n  * [Contact us](https://universalquantum.com/contact-us)\n\n\n[Privacy](https://universalquantum.com/privacy-policy)\n\u00a9 2026 Universal Quantum Ltd.  \n\n![](https://universalquantum.com/sites/default/files/inline-images/footer.png)\n",
