niversal Quantum, the UK based company building the world's most scalable quantum computers, today announced the appointment of Freeke Heijman as Senior European Advisor.</span></p>  </div>\n\n        <a href=\"/knowledge-hub/universal-quantum-appoints-Freeke-Heijman-as-senior-european-advisor\" class=\"cta-link cta-link--teaser spacer-double\" rel=\"bookmark\">Read more</a>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"column--full column--three-fifths-md\">\n        <a href=\"/knowledge-hub/universal-quantum-appoints-Freeke-Heijman-as-senior-european-advisor\" class=\"bare-link\" rel=\"bookmark\"><div class=\"field field--image field--label-hidden field__item\">\n              <picture>\n                  <source srcset=\"/sites/default/files/styles/landscape_desktop/public/2026-05/52995517310_bba4d9d357_c.jpg?h=2379611a&amp;itok=ibql1SqM 1x\" media=\"all and (min-width: 1320px)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" width=\"1650\" height=\"707\">\n              <source srcset=\"/sites/default/files/styles/landscape_tablet/public/2026-05/52995517310_bba4d9d357_c.jpg?h=2379611a&amp;itok=1JHjiVEm 1x\" media=\"all and (min-width: 768px)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" width=\"798\" height=\"342\">\n              <source srcset=\"/sites/default/files/styles/banner_mobile/public/2026-05/52995517310_bba4d9d357_c.jpg?h=c05c9e62&amp;itok=GqfA8Xjr 1x\" type=\"image/jpeg\" width=\"533\" height=\"533\">\n                  <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"/sites/default/files/styles/landscape_desktop/public/2026-05/52995517310_bba4d9d357_c.jpg?h=2379611a&amp;itok=ibql1SqM\" width=\"1650\" height=\"707\" alt=\"UQ\" class=\"round\">\n\n  </picture>\n\n  </div>\n</a>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </article>\n\n</div>\n    <div class=\"view__row\">\n \n\n  <article class=\"node node--large-teaser node--type-article\">\n    <div class=\"columns columns--middle\">\n      <div class=\"column column--two-fifths-md stack--single teaser__content\">\n        <h3 class=\"h5 text-bold teaser__title\">Podcast: The Wiring Problem in Large-Scale Quantum Computers</h3>\n        <div class=\"clearfix field--formatted field field--preview-text field--label-hidden field--text-long field__item\">\n          <p><span class=\"sc-fzUa-dk gFqrs text-pink\" data-slate-node=\"text\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\" data-slate-string=\"true\">This episode explores the challenges of wiring and control systems in large-scale quantum computers, drawing parallels with classical electronics and physics labs.</span></p>  </div>\n\n        <a href=\"/knowledge-hub/podcast/the-wiring-problem-in-large-scale-quantum-computers\" class=\"cta-link cta-link--teaser spacer-double\" rel=\"bookmark\">Read more</a>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"column--full column--three-fifths-md\">\n        <a href=\"/knowledge-hub/podcast/the-wiring-problem-in-large-scale-quantum-computers\" class=\"bare-link\" rel=\"bookmark\"><div class=\"field field--image field--label-hidden field__item\">\n              <picture>\n                  <source srcset=\"/sites/default/files/styles/landscape_desktop/public/2026-04/Logo%202.jpg?h=f697827c&amp;itok=LUx1fMG3 1x\" media=\"all and (min-width: 1320px)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" width=\"1650\" height=\"707\">\n              <source srcset=\"/sites/default/files/styles/landscape_tablet/public/2026-04/Logo%202.jpg?h=f697827c&amp;itok=33A-ydug 1x\" media=\"all and (min-width: 768px)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" width=\"1320\" height=\"566\">\n              <source srcset=\"/sites/default/files/styles/banner_mobile/public/2026-04/Logo%202.jpg?h=d0e75635&amp;itok=H9kGYiNn 1x\" type=\"image/jpeg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1024\">\n                  <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"/sites/default/files/styles/landscape_desktop/public/2026-04/Logo%202.jpg?h=f697827c&amp;itok=LUx1fMG3\" width=\"1650\" height=\"707\" alt=\"UQ\" class=\"round\">\n\n  </picture>\n\n  </div>\n</a>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </article>\n\n</div>\n    <div class=\"view__row\">\n \n\n  <article class=\"node node--large-teaser node--type-article\">\n    <div class=\"columns columns--middle\">\n      <div class=\"column column--two-fifths-md stack--single teaser__content\">\n        <h3 class=\"h5 text-bold teaser__title\">Podcast: \u00a32B and What Actually Matters</h3>\n        <div class=\"clearfix field--formatted field field--preview-text field--label-hidden field--text-long field__item\">\n          <p><span class=\"text-pink\">This episode explores the UK government's recent \u00a32 billion quantum funding announcement, delving into quantum technology missions, misconceptions about quantum computing and its potential impact on industry and society.</span></p>  </div>\n\n        <a href=\"/knowledge-hub/podcast/%C2%A32B-and-what-actually-matters\" class=\"cta-link cta-link--teaser spacer-double\" rel=\"bookmark\">Read more</a>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"column--full column--three-fifths-md\">\n        <a href=\"/knowledge-hub/podcast/%C2%A32B-and-what-actually-matters\" class=\"bare-link\" rel=\"bookmark\"><div class=\"field field--image field--label-hidden field__item\">\n              <picture>\n                  <source srcset=\"/sites/default/files/styles/landscape_desktop/public/2026-03/Logo%202.jpg?h=e55433bc&amp;itok=0zyp0EBf 1x\" media=\"all and (min-width: 1320px)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" width=\"1650\" height=\"707\">\n              <source srcset=\"/sites/default/files/styles/landscape_tablet/public/2026-03/Logo%202.jpg?h=e55433bc&amp;itok=1c-u39Ul 1x\" media=\"all and (min-width: 768px)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" width=\"1320\" height=\"565\">\n              <source srcset=\"/sites/default/files/styles/banner_mobile/public/2026-03/Logo%202.jpg?h=d0e75635&amp;itok=Szuqljc8 1x\" type=\"image/jpeg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1024\">\n                  <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"/sites/default/files/styles/landscape_desktop/public/2026-03/Logo%202.jpg?h=e55433bc&amp;itok=0zyp0EBf\" width=\"1650\" height=\"707\" alt=\"UQ\" class=\"round\">\n\n  </picture>\n\n  </div>\n</a>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n 